        </p>
            <div data-seq="274286785" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">百里山水画中游</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274287276">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12672.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="延庆" target="_blank">延庆</a>百里山水画廊景区位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12672.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="延庆" target="_blank">延庆</a>区<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16215.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="东北" target="_blank">东北</a>部千家店镇，景区包括一环三区十二个空间节点，有<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15091.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="淮北" target="_blank">淮北</a>山水之美，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="黄山" target="_blank">黄山</a>之松，兔耳岭之草甸，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="苏州" target="_blank">苏州</a>之美观。涉及滨河环线112华里，“百里山水画廊”因此得名。<br />
<br />
早春季节前往百里山水画廊是一件十分惬意之事。春风拂面、阳光下生机盎然。车行路上完全是一种享受，在这里远离了大都市的喧嚣，身心都会得到极大放松。<br />
<br />
详见我的游纪《百里山水画中游》；&nbsp;&nbsp;链接：<a href="http://www.mafengwo.cn/i/7008023.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">http://www.mafengwo.cn/i/7008023.html</a><br />
<br />
标志性的建筑
        </p>
